  "requirementText": "The computational model shall be deemed acceptable for regulatory submission when the predicted relative hemolysis index RH does not exceed 1.12 across all evaluated operating conditions, where RH is defined as the ratio of predicted device NIH to the predicate device NIH measured under equivalent flow conditions.",
  "hasCredibilityFactor": [
    {
