      "rationale": "Blood density (1060 kg/m³) and dynamic viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s) sourced from ISO 10993-4 reference values. Pump geometry dimensions taken from FDA benchmark CAD files with dimensional tolerances ±0.05 mm. Inlet flow rates and rotational speeds set to match experimental conditions with documented traceability to calibrated instrumentation."
