    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The predicted RH values across all five operating points remain below the acceptance threshold specified in the requirement, supporting the regulatory submission decision. No credibility gaps were identified that would preclude acceptance.",
